## 2. Acceptance criteria

- [ ] Training script runs end-to-end with `uv run python src/train.py`
- [ ] Evaluation metrics reported in a structured way (no print-debugging only)
- [ ] Notebooks under `notebooks/` are reproducible (kernel + dataset version pinned)
- [ ] Model artifacts (weights, configs) saved to `models/` with timestamps
- [ ] `uv run pytest tests/` covers data-pipeline transforms

## 3. Non-goals

- No production serving — that's a separate project (likely python-fastapi)
- No cloud orchestration — local + single-GPU training is the scope
- No proprietary datasets in the repo — store under git-LFS or external bucket

